ac-ip.help: IP address of the validation controller that AP must be able to join after applying AP local configuration.
ac-ip.name: ac-ip

ac-port.help: Port of the validation controller that AP must be able to join after applying AP local configuration (1024 - 49150, default = 5246).
ac-port.name: ac-port

ac-timer.help: Maximum waiting time for the AP to join the validation controller after applying AP local configuration (3 - 30 min, default = 10).
ac-timer.name: ac-timer

options.help: This controller is the one and only controller that the AP could join after applying AP local configuration.
options.name: default

options.help: Specified controller is the one and only controller that the AP could join after applying AP local configuration.
options.name: specify

options.help: Any controller defined by AP local configuration after applying AP local configuration.
options.name: apcfg

passwd-value.help: AP local configuration command password value.
passwd-value.name: passwd-value
